# question_bank_engine is a separate service run from its own local venv —
# that venv (and its runtime ChromaDB/embedding-cache data) was being swept
# into the build context and then COPY'd wholesale into this image, bloating
# it by 1GB+ per build and, on a disk-constrained host, failing the build
# outright while unpacking it. Anchored explicitly (not just "venv"/"data")
# since bare patterns weren't reliably excluding this nested path.
**/venv
**/.venv
question_bank_engine/data
